				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Kh%E1%BA%A3i-Si%C3%AAu/Duy-t%C3%A2m/poem-84I5txTK3YcSVWYsFSEj7A">Duy tâm - 唯心</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Kh%E1%BA%A3i-Si%C3%AAu/author-v6D2LCbIpae0gM4Dq3ytUA">Lương Khải Siêu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%C3%A1n-Si%C3%AAu/Ho%C3%A1-Ch%C3%A2u-t%C3%A1c/poem-0PGPfUjA1jcv-L13UicFdg">Hoá Châu tác - 化州作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%C3%A1n-Si%C3%AAu/author-8OezdZDSC-q-9wfu_BOuVw">Trương Hán Siêu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Ho%E1%BA%A1-%C4%91%C3%A1p-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-4-Ho%E1%BA%A1-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-chu%E1%BB%B7-%C3%B4/poem-53ZjAXi8lSNpGs0f1TVm6g">Hoạ đáp thi kỳ 4 - Hoạ đại chuỷ ô - 和答詩其四－和大觜烏</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/Ho%E1%BA%A1-k%C3%AA-ti%C3%AAn/poem-mhyNtBRunJcN6rVFhRvyJA">Hoạ kê tiên - 和乩仙</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Gi%E1%BA%A3n/Long-M%C3%B4n-than/poem-aq7Xlki-ZiKUgiWo_BOxNg">Long Môn than - 龍門灘</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Gi%E1%BA%A3n/author--99oPAxPzhbe5OwOvLz_qg">Lê Giản</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/Tam-nguy%E1%BB%87t-h%E1%BB%91i-nh%E1%BA%ADt-giang-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-ng%C3%A2m/poem-zYmrmVjGfWGYYyDsr-JUPw">Tam nguyệt hối nhật giang thượng ngâm - 三月晦日江上吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/author-t0ibbyX9M2Hpw0m6n5VY-Q">Nguyễn Văn Siêu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/T%E1%BA%A3o-mai-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-ekjgWfNzYaR2dtLmQkchqQ">Tảo mai kỳ 1 - 早梅其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/author-EY7jN0xHQfiiJpD91KwIgw">Trần Nhân Tông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/Th%E1%BA%A1ch-c%E1%BB%95-ca/poem-SQLcZneUoty6Zn7UCfgM4Q">Thạch cổ ca - 石鼓歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/author-mXDKUZpgHTE66OhltBCLIw">Hàn Dũ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Thanh-Giang-t%E1%BB%B1-t%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BB%AD/poem-LbRek2l0TIlfncpkxqfX1g">Thanh Giang tự tị thử - 清江寺避暑</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-An-xu%C3%A2n-m%E1%BB%99/poem-EfveM4kJVW--oriWHDFL-A">Trường An xuân mộ - 長安春暮</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/author-l-NINz3JTJVTCX2aN0HlSQ">Thái Thuận</a>)<br></div>	</div>
